OL,5,
OL,6,FJust what are STV's proposals for
OL,7,Fchanges to its news service?
OL,9,FWe know the broadcaster plans to stop
OL,10,Fproducing a separate programme for the
OL,11,Fformer Grampian area.
OL,13,FInstead a programme for both Central
OL,14,Fand Northern Scotland will be produced
OL,15,Fand presented from Glasgow.
OL,17,FBut beyond that very little appears to
OL,18,Fhave been said publicly.
OL,20,FIt is reported that the company wants
OL,21,Fto cut 60 jobs including 30 in news.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
