OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV
OL,4,Ccuts ` but what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FNothing appears to have been said
OL,7,Fpublicly to clarify just what roles are
OL,8,Ffacing the axe. Are all the job cuts in
OL,9,FAberdeen?
OL,11,FNor has anything been said publicly to
OL,12,Fconfirm what the new programme would
OL,13,Flook like.
OL,15,FSTV has just spent good money revamping
OL,16,Fthe look of its news service.
OL,18,FMy guess is we might end up with the
OL,19,Fcurrent Central Belt programme with
OL,20,Fsome stories from the north of Scotland
OL,21,Fwithin the mix.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
