OL,3,GOPINIONCLittle information about STV
OL,4,Ccuts ` but what are the options?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt will not feel obviously different to
OL,7,Fviewers in Glasgow and Edinburgh.
OL,9,FThe proposed changes have been widely
OL,10,Fcondemned by politicians in the north
OL,11,Fof Scotland.
OL,13,FBut will Ofcom ` if it is so minded `
OL,14,Fsave Grampian?
OL,16,FIt is possible they will reject STV's
OL,17,Fplan outright. Past experience though
OL,18,Fsuggests this is unlikely. It would
OL,19,Falso be humiliating for STV management.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
