OL,5,
OL,6,FRealistically they'll either say yes or
OL,7,Fbroker some compromise. Perhaps
OL,8,Fpre-recorded localised bulletins at
OL,9,F1.55pm and 10.30pm plus a pre-recorded
OL,10,Fsub-opt within the 6pm programme. (At
OL,11,Fthe weekend both regions get a joint
OL,12,Fbulletin from Glasgow.)
OL,14,FBut I cannot see Ofcom insisting that
OL,15,Fany remaining programme for the north
OL,16,Fneeds to be presented from Aberdeen.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
