OL,5,
OL,6,FThey cannot be inconsistent with what
OL,7,Flicensees are or are not allowed to do.
OL,8,FThink Border from Gateshead,
OL,9,FWestcountry from Bristol, the East
OL,10,FMidlands from Birmingham.
OL,12,FI don't think, however, that a
OL,13,Fcompletely recorded programme would be
OL,14,Fright or practical.
OL,16,FSTV North does show some Scottish
OL,17,Fnational news, especially politics. A
OL,18,F5pm recording would mean a much poorer
OL,19,Fservice.
