OL,5,
OL,6,FBut a 10-minute recorded section within
OL,7,Fthe programme focused on regional news
OL,8,Fcould work ` even if it might be
OL,9,Fundesirable. Big stories or developing
OL,10,Fstories can go in the live part of the
OL,11,Fprogramme.
OL,13,FOfcom's consultation should reveal more
OL,14,Fdetails of the plan plus the possible
OL,15,Ftimescale for a decision and, if
OL,16,Fagreed, changes.
OL,18,FThe public needs to be fully involved
OL,19,Fin this consultation.
