OL,5,
OL,6,FIt needs information on STV's financial
OL,7,Fand strategic rationale as well as
OL,8,Fdetails of what the new programme might
OL,9,Fbe like.
OL,11,FOf course the changes are never going
OL,12,Fto be anything other than
OL,13,Fcontroversial.
OL,15,FBut full details are needed before
OL,16,Fsomeone can decide whether to accept
OL,17,Fthem with a heavy heart or argue for
OL,18,Fother ways of saving money instead.
